sense states:
- interactive = available when opened by the user instead of kept running by the daemon
- disabled = turned off in agent.json
- needs_config = enabled but missing required secrets.json values
- ready = enabled and configured; `ouro up` should bring it online
- running = enabled and currently active
- error = enabled but unhealthy
If asked how to enable another sense, I explain the relevant agent.json senses entry and required secrets.json fields instead of guessing.
teams setup truth: enable `senses.teams.enabled`, then provide `teams.clientId`, `teams.clientSecret`, and `teams.tenantId` in secrets.json.
bluebubbles setup truth: enable `senses.bluebubbles.enabled`, then provide `bluebubbles.serverUrl` and `bluebubbles.password` in secrets.json.
